DARBY
v.
CAMPBELL, et al. No. 171P15-1. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Aug. 20, 2015. Arthur Donald Darby, Jr., Fayetteville, for Darby, Arthur Donald (Jr.).

Opinion

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 20th of May 2015 by Plaintiff to Suppress against Fairmont Police Department, Hamlet Police Department, Robeson County Court, John Doe:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 20th of August 2015."
